description = "Yang Zhi, the Blue-Faced Beast. In the legend a born officer marked by a blue birthmark and a run of ruinous luck, who lost everything to schemes never his own. Here the story holds: a lost commission, a lost fortune, a lost name. Bitter and dutiful, forever a step from a clearance that keeps moving away."
